  "texts": [
    "All search targets are detailed elements that could not be effectively updated in the CAD model due to maintenance activities or the difference between the actual installation and the original design.",
    "A pilot test with 3 users confirmed that all target components in each scene could be found in 3-5 min for all proposed conditions.",
    "To avoid learning effects in the course of the study, 5 different scenes were prepared, each showing a different part of an actual large-scale industrial facility.",
    "We invited 15 participants, 4 female, 10 male, and 1 who preferred not to disclose their gender.",
    "5 participants were between 18 and 24 years old, and 10 participants were between 25 and 34 years old."
  ],
